description: It may not be your truck (it’s theirs) but the heaping platters of deliciously meaty and cheesy nachos they’re piling up are all yours to dig into. It’s Nacho Truck is serving up the streets of Sacramento with gourmet nachos that are so top notch, every single chip you pick will have a perfect portion of tasty toppings. “Pig Out!” on their scrumptious braised pork nachos, topped with black beans, green onion, diced apple, fontina cheddar, and sriracha cream. Glimpse the yummy life of a “Bad A** Mediterranean” and get into some pita chips topped with leg of lamb, refried black beans, kalamata olives, goat cheese, mint cream with lemon zest. And there’s more! When it comes to this truck, hunger is nacho problem.
name: It's Nacho Truck
